#. <section class="sutta" id="sn12.2"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn12.2:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 12"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 12"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn12.2:0.2"
msgid "1. Buddhavagga"
msgstr "1. The Buddhas"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn12.2:0.3"
msgid "2. Vibhaṅgasutta"
msgstr "2. Analysis"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthiyaṃ viharati."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn12.2:1.2"
msgid "“Paṭiccasamuppādaṃ vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi vibhajissāmi."
msgstr "“Mendicants, I will teach and analyze for you dependent origination."

msgctxt "sn12.2:1.3"
msgid "Taṃ suṇātha, sādhukaṃ manasi karotha, bhāsissāmī”ti."
msgstr "Listen and pay close attention, I will speak.”"

msgctxt "sn12.2:1.4"
msgid "“Evaṃ, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhū bhagavato paccassosuṃ."
msgstr "“Yes, sir,” they replied."

msgctxt "sn12.2:1.5"
msgid "Bhagavā etadavoca:"
msgstr "The Buddha said this:"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:2.1"
msgid "“Katamo ca, bhikkhave, paṭiccasamuppādo?"
msgstr "“And what is dependent origination?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.2"
msgid "Avijjāpaccayā, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "Ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.3"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ;"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.4"
msgid "viññāṇapaccayā nāmarūpaṃ;"
msgstr "Consciousness is a condition for name and form."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.5"
msgid "nāmarūpapaccayā saḷāyatanaṃ;"
msgstr "Name and form are conditions for the six sense fields."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.6"
msgid "saḷāyatanapaccayā phasso;"
msgstr "The six sense fields are conditions for contact."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.7"
msgid "phassapaccayā vedanā;"
msgstr "Contact is a condition for feeling."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.8"
msgid "vedanāpaccayā taṇhā;"
msgstr "Feeling is a condition for craving."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.9"
msgid "taṇhāpaccayā upādānaṃ;"
msgstr "Craving is a condition for grasping."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.10"
msgid "upādānapaccayā bhavo;"
msgstr "Grasping is a condition for continued existence."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.11"
msgid "bhavapaccayā jāti;"
msgstr "Continued existence is a condition for rebirth."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.12"
msgid "jātipaccayā jarāmaraṇaṃ sokaparidevadukkhadomanassupāyāsā sambhavanti."
msgstr ""
"Rebirth is a condition for old age and death, sorrow, lamentation, pain, "
"sadness, and distress to come to be."

msgctxt "sn12.2:2.13"
msgid "Evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.3"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:3.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, jarāmaraṇaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is old age and death?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:3.2"
msgid ""
"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhi tamhi sattanikāye jarā jīraṇatā khaṇḍiccaṃ "
"pāliccaṃ valittacatā āyuno saṃhāni indriyānaṃ paripāko;"
msgstr ""
"The old age, decrepitude, broken teeth, grey hair, wrinkly skin, diminished "
"vitality, and failing faculties of the various sentient beings in the "
"various orders of sentient beings."

msgctxt "sn12.2:3.3"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati jarā."
msgstr "This is called old age."

#. VAR: () → (jīvitindriyassa upacchedo) (s1-3, km)
msgctxt "sn12.2:3.4"
msgid ""
"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhā tamhā sattanikāyā cuti cavanatā bhedo "
"antaradhānaṃ maccu maraṇaṃ kālakiriyā khandhānaṃ bhedo kaḷevarassa nikkhepo "
"(), "
msgstr ""
"The passing away, perishing, disintegration, demise, mortality, death, "
"decease, breaking up of the aggregates, and laying to rest of the corpse of "
"the various sentient beings in the various orders of sentient beings. "

msgctxt "sn12.2:3.5"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati maraṇaṃ."
msgstr "This is called death."

msgctxt "sn12.2:3.6"
msgid "Iti ayañca jarā, idañca maraṇaṃ."
msgstr "Such is old age, and such is death."

msgctxt "sn12.2:3.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, jarāmaraṇaṃ."
msgstr "This is called old age and death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:4.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, jāti?"
msgstr "And what is rebirth?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:4.2"
msgid ""
"Yā tesaṃ tesaṃ sattānaṃ tamhi tamhi sattanikāye jāti sañjāti okkanti "
"abhinibbatti khandhānaṃ pātubhāvo āyatanānaṃ paṭilābho."
msgstr ""
"The rebirth, inception, conception, reincarnation, manifestation of the "
"aggregates, and acquisition of the sense fields of the various sentient "
"beings in the various orders of sentient beings."

msgctxt "sn12.2:4.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, jāti."
msgstr "This is called rebirth."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:5.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, bhavo?"
msgstr "And what is continued existence?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:5.2"
msgid "Tayome, bhikkhave, bhavā—"
msgstr "There are these three states of existence."

msgctxt "sn12.2:5.3"
msgid "kāmabhavo, rūpabhavo, arūpabhavo."
msgstr ""
"Existence in the sensual realm, the realm of luminous form, and the formless "
"realm."

msgctxt "sn12.2:5.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, bhavo."
msgstr "This is called continued existence."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:6.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, upādānaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is grasping?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:6.2"
msgid "Cattārimāni, bhikkhave, upādānāni—"
msgstr "There are these four kinds of grasping."

msgctxt "sn12.2:6.3"
msgid "kāmupādānaṃ, diṭṭhupādānaṃ, sīlabbatupādānaṃ, attavādupādānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Grasping at sensual pleasures, views, precepts and observances, and theories "
"of a self."

msgctxt "sn12.2:6.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, upādānaṃ."
msgstr "This is called grasping."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:7.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, taṇhā?"
msgstr "And what is craving?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:7.2"
msgid "Chayime, bhikkhave, taṇhākāyā—"
msgstr "There are these six classes of craving."

msgctxt "sn12.2:7.3"
msgid ""
"rūpataṇhā, saddataṇhā, gandhataṇhā, rasataṇhā, phoṭṭhabbataṇhā, dhammataṇhā."
msgstr "Craving for sights, sounds, smells, tastes, touches, and thoughts."

msgctxt "sn12.2:7.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, taṇhā."
msgstr "This is called craving."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc8"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:8.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, vedanā?"
msgstr "And what is feeling?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:8.2"
msgid "Chayime, bhikkhave, vedanākāyā—"
msgstr "There are these six classes of feeling."

msgctxt "sn12.2:8.3"
msgid ""
"cakkhusamphassajā vedanā, sotasamphassajā vedanā, ghānasamphassajā vedanā, "
"jivhāsamphassajā vedanā, kāyasamphassajā vedanā, manosamphassajā vedanā."
msgstr ""
"Feeling born of contact through the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind."

msgctxt "sn12.2:8.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, vedanā."
msgstr "This is called feeling."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc9"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:9.1"
msgid "Katamo ca, bhikkhave, phasso?"
msgstr "And what is contact?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:9.2"
msgid "Chayime, bhikkhave, phassakāyā—"
msgstr "There are these six classes of contact."

msgctxt "sn12.2:9.3"
msgid ""
"cakkhusamphasso, sotasamphasso, ghānasamphasso, jivhāsamphasso, "
"kāyasamphasso, manosamphasso."
msgstr "Contact through the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind."

msgctxt "sn12.2:9.4"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, phasso."
msgstr "This is called contact."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc10"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:10.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, saḷāyatanaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are the six sense fields?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:10.2"
msgid ""
"Cakkhāyatanaṃ, sotāyatanaṃ, ghānāyatanaṃ, jivhāyatanaṃ, kāyāyatanaṃ, "
"manāyatanaṃ—"
msgstr "The sense fields of the eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind."

msgctxt "sn12.2:10.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, saḷāyatanaṃ."
msgstr "These are called the six sense fields."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli2.4"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc11"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:11.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, nāmarūpaṃ?"
msgstr "And what are name and form?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.2"
msgid "Vedanā, saññā, cetanā, phasso, manasikāro—"
msgstr "Feeling, perception, intention, contact, and focus."

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.3"
msgid "idaṃ vuccati nāmaṃ."
msgstr "This is called name."

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.4"
msgid "Cattāro ca mahābhūtā, catunnañca mahābhūtānaṃ upādāyarūpaṃ."
msgstr ""
"The four primary elements, and form derived from the four primary elements."

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.5"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati rūpaṃ."
msgstr "This is called form."

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.6"
msgid "Iti idañca nāmaṃ, idañca rūpaṃ."
msgstr "Such is name and such is form."

msgctxt "sn12.2:11.7"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, nāmarūpaṃ."
msgstr "These are called name and form."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc12"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:12.1"
msgid "Katamañca, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṃ?"
msgstr "And what is consciousness?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:12.2"
msgid "Chayime, bhikkhave, viññāṇakāyā—"
msgstr "There are these six classes of consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.2:12.3"
msgid ""
"cakkhuviññāṇaṃ, sotaviññāṇaṃ, ghānaviññāṇaṃ, jivhāviññāṇaṃ, kāyaviññāṇaṃ, "
"manoviññāṇaṃ."
msgstr "Eye, ear, nose, tongue, body, and mind consciousness."

msgctxt "sn12.2:12.4"
msgid "Idaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, viññāṇaṃ."
msgstr "This is called consciousness."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc13"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:13.1"
msgid "Katame ca, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā?"
msgstr "And what are choices?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:13.2"
msgid "Tayome, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā—"
msgstr "There are three kinds of choices."

msgctxt "sn12.2:13.3"
msgid "kāyasaṅkhāro, vacīsaṅkhāro, cittasaṅkhāro."
msgstr "Choices by way of body, speech, and mind."

msgctxt "sn12.2:13.4"
msgid "Ime vuccanti, bhikkhave, saṅkhārā."
msgstr "These are called choices."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc14"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:14.1"
msgid "Katamā ca, bhikkhave, avijjā?"
msgstr "And what is ignorance?"

msgctxt "sn12.2:14.2"
msgid ""
"Yaṃ kho, bhikkhave, dukkhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe "
"aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇaṃ."
msgstr ""
"Not knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn12.2:14.3"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, bhikkhave, avijjā."
msgstr "This is called ignorance."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc15"></a>
msgctxt "sn12.2:15.1"
msgid "Iti kho, bhikkhave, avijjāpaccayā saṅkhārā;"
msgstr "And so, ignorance is a condition for choices."

msgctxt "sn12.2:15.2"
msgid "saṅkhārapaccayā viññāṇaṃ … pe …"
msgstr "Choices are a condition for consciousness. …"

msgctxt "sn12.2:15.3"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa samudayo hoti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering originates."

msgctxt "sn12.2:15.4"
msgid "Avijjāya tveva asesavirāganirodhā saṅkhāranirodho;"
msgstr ""
"When ignorance fades away and ceases with nothing left over, choices cease."

msgctxt "sn12.2:15.5"
msgid "saṅkhāranirodhā viññāṇanirodho … pe …"
msgstr "When choices cease, consciousness ceases. …"

msgctxt "sn12.2:15.6"
msgid "evametassa kevalassa dukkhakkhandhassa nirodho hotī”ti."
msgstr "That is how this entire mass of suffering ceases.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn12.2:15.7"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
